@James - Nice. (and true) :)

@missgiggles - There are loads of specialties that can live under the umbrella of Graphic Design; identity design, interface design, publication design, information design, and so on.

I usually only call myself a graphic designer in when speaking to people who either wouldn’t get the specifics or wouldn’t care. :) Doctors are a (somewhat) reasonable analogy. Most of them practice within a specialty or sub-specialty like cardiology, neurology, etc. When asked what they do for a living, much of the time they’ll just tell you they’re “a doctor”.
